Dashboard Objectives
Provide hospital management with:
•	Real-time occupancy visibility
•	Forecasted bed demand
•	OT utilization analysis
•	Department bottlenecks
•	Wait time reduction insights
________________________________________
Dashboard Components
VisualPurpose
Gauge Chart	ICU occupancy percentage
KPI Cards	Active patients / available beds
Line Chart	Weekly forecast trend
Heatmap	Department bottlenecks
Drill-through	Department-level details
Slicer	Ward / Department filter
